<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/27189872-an-american-genocide"><img alt="An American Genocide: The United States and the California Indian Catastrophe, 1846-1873" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1458172561l/27189872._SX98_.jpg" />
